Hey man,

Im always in or around the Oasis of Marr with my Cleric (Level 17) I thinkwe
could make a pretty sweet combo. My Clerics name on Solusek Ro is Rayne look
for me ill be online in about 3 hours or so .... ill look for you then. I
can either take you to the Oasis or we could head to Guk, which is also good
for exp. Lemme know what you think.

Rayne/Lothaniel T'kazz
